title: Jean Michel Jarre Radio special Dutch Radio 4

Jean Michel Jarre Radio special Dutch Radio 4
---------------------------------------------

The Dutch Radio station Radio 4 had a three part special about
the french synthesizer musician Jean Michel Jarre.

The tracklisting of these parts:

=======

4FM MUZIKALE DELICATESSEN (MUSICAL DELICACIES)
Thursday 25th April 2006: 00:00-01:00 (Midnight-1am) (Local Time)

[01] EROSMACHINE (3'00)
[02] BONJOUR, HELLO (25:57)
[03] WHISPERS OF LIFE (25:57)
